# This repo exists ONLY so the Nix flake here is a "git flake": nix then copies
# just the git-tracked files into the store on `nix develop`, instead of the
# entire ~60G working tree (build/, swift/, llvm-project/, …) which filled the
# disk. Ignore everything except the flake files themselves.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/flake.nix
!/flake.lock
